      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source of spare parts. The engine currently suffers from significant oil leaks and chronic overheating, likely indicating a failing head gasket, and the transmission shifts roughly between gears. Externally, the body shows signs of heavy wear, including noticeable rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior requires a complete overhaul due to torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, and I recommend towing it from the lot.",
